headline: Does Williams Companies Still Offer Value After Strong Multi Year Share Price Gains?
summary: Wondering if Williams Companies at around $59 is still a smart buy or if most of the upside is gone? Here is a look at what the market might be pricing in and where the hidden value, or risk, could be lurking. The stock has edged up about 1.1% over the last week and is roughly flat over 30 days, but it is still up 6.4% year to date and 12.7% over the past year, with long term gains of 107.6% over three years and 281.5% over five years.
